\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He said quietly to Seb, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Can I ask why I\u8217\'92m here?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I only ask because I know there\u8217\'92s no love for the Hrkan world out here in the Sand. I\u8217\'92ve no love for it either. But if you intend to use me as a weapon as they were, I\u8217\'92m not going to cooperate.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That so?\u8221\'94 Seb asked with an inattentive sigh.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ve no intention of letting you use me to kill people.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Seb was unimpressed. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I saw ya kill three men with one swipe of that Mazidfire.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That was against my will.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Then what ya wanna do don\u8217\'92t matter, does it?\u8221\'94}}